				<h3 id="others-title">3. Others</h3>
				<div id="global-options-section" class="awards">
					<p>Here are included the descriptions of same words.</p>
					<ul>
						<li id="ticks-explanation"><strong>Tick:</strong> A tick is the unit used by DMDX to time screen displays and the time it takes the cathode ray on the monitor to scanthe tube.
							<p>11.80 milliseconds on the desktop machines in the testing rooms</p>
							<p>16.67 milliseconds on the portable machines</p></li>
						<li id="color-indication-explanation"><strong>Colors indication:</strong> The colors must be indicated in RGB scale. This is done with three numbers from 0 to 255 been the first number the amount of red, the second the omount of green and the third the amount of blue. Some examples:
							<p>255000000 is red</p>
							<p>000255000 is green</p>
							<p>255255255 is white</p>
							<p>000000000 is black</p></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
